TopicTitle: Crash Log with mods. New to KSP, please help?

Articles.Content:
Recently downloaded KSP for my mac, but encountered a problem. I was running quite a few mods that worked before but without reason stopped working. Same as they had been when they were working. It appears to be a texture loading issue with a default part, so i reinstalled KSP and added the mods back in with no avail. Of course the vanilla worked. Thanks for help, log below.
